tween 40 and 50 percent, roughly three times higher than in the West Bank. </p><figure><a href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1a599e13-4540-4db0-9d47-e019c4fdb11d_604x590.png" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/3HBtY-FAoMxFtZcyM8JJhzK6mEEMXY3jKvgBg4_UK6w=/aHR0cHM6Ly9zdWJzdGFja2Nkbi5jb20vaW1hZ2UvZmV0Y2gvd180MjQsY19saW1pdCxmX3dlYnAscV9hdXRvOmdvb2QsZmxfcHJvZ3Jlc3NpdmU6c3RlZXAvaHR0cHMlM0ElMkYlMkZzdWJzdGFjay1wb3N0LW1lZGlhLnMzLmFtYXpvbmF3cy5jb20lMkZwdWJsaWMlMkZpbWFnZXMlMkYxYTU5OWUxMy00NTQwLTRkYjAtOWQ0Ny1lMDE5YzRmZGIxMWRfNjA0eDU5MC5wbmc= 424w, https://reader.miniflux. 848w, https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/d6Yl5EBXHvGKu_Rmua-EbjLmgUvNkxLQZoASAAGE_Ow=/aHR0cHM6Ly9zdWJzdGFja2Nkbi5jb20vaW1hZ2UvZmV0Y2gvd18xMjcyLGNfbGltaXQsZl93ZWJwLHFfYXV0bzpnb29kLGZsX3Byb2dyZXNzaXZlOnN0ZWVwL2h0dHBzJTNBJTJGJTJGc3Vic3RhY2stcG9zdC1tZWRpYS5zMy5hbWF6b25hd3MuY29tJTJGcHVibGljJTJGaW1hZ2VzJTJGMWE1OTllMTMtNDU0MC00ZGIwLTlkNDctZTAxOWM0ZmRiMTFkXzYwNHg1OTAucG5n 1272w, https://reader.miniflux. 1456w" sizes="100vw"/><img src="https://reader.miniflux." width="604" height="590" alt="" title="" srcset="https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/YYm0FHLu1aVjfPUl4N14POVHkT-8-ywgMyvqcnNvzpc=/aHR0cHM6Ly9zdWJzdGFja2Nkbi5jb20vaW1hZ2UvZmV0Y2gvd180MjQsY19saW1pdCxmX2F1dG8scV9hdXRvOmdvb2QsZmxfcHJvZ3Jlc3NpdmU6c3RlZXAvaHR0cHMlM0ElMkYlMkZzdWJzdGFjay1wb3N0LW1lZGlhLnMzLmFtYXpvbmF3cy5jb20lMkZwdWJsaWMlMkZpbWFnZXMlMkYxYTU5OWUxMy00NTQwLTRkYjAtOWQ0Ny1lMDE5YzRmZGIxMWRfNjA0eDU5MC5wbmc= 424w, https://reader.miniflux. 848w, https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/eZTz42- 1272w, https://reader.miniflux. 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"/></picture></a></figure><p>As Shir Hever’s data show, wages in Gaza stagnate at the very bottom of the racialized pyramid in Israel/Palestine. </p><figure><a href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F98a1e55d-7883-4c67-8d7b-6e024309fed5_1166x646.png" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/pwsgBnya2akTB-ku8FfLQ3QEze_zmPAculsg8-_8ucY=/aHR0cHM6Ly9zdWJzdGFja2Nkbi5jb20vaW1hZ2UvZmV0Y2gvd180MjQsY19saW1pdCxmX3dlYnAscV9hdXRvOmdvb2QsZmxfcHJvZ3Jlc3NpdmU6c3RlZXAvaHR0cHMlM0ElMkYlMkZzdWJzdGFjay1wb3N0LW1lZGlhLnMzLmFtYXpvbmF3cy5jb20lMkZwdWJsaWMlMkZpbWFnZXMlMkY5OGExZTU1ZC03ODgzLTRjNjctOGQ3Yi02ZTAyNDMwOWZlZDVfMTE2Nng2NDYucG5n 424w, https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/OLo51N5O8fkiYgWXzdcabJKxTPqeNogHlyI-h8h5Mc8=/aHR0cHM6Ly9zdWJzdGFja2Nkbi5jb20vaW1hZ2UvZmV0Y2gvd184NDgsY19saW1pdCxmX3dlYnAscV9hdXRvOmdvb2QsZmxfcHJvZ3Jlc3NpdmU6c3RlZXAvaHR0cHMlM0ElMkYlMkZzdWJzdGFjay1wb3N0LW1lZGlhLnMzLmFtYXpvbmF3cy5jb20lMkZwdWJsaWMlMkZpbWFnZXMlMkY5OGExZTU1ZC03ODgzLTRjNjctOGQ3Yi02ZTAyNDMwOWZlZDVfMTE2Nng2NDYucG5n 848w, https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/_kqbVDwu47hpYkLy- 1272w, https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/tPsL4kzvoFIwjrl86Lljz8dJlDRCEz-h-54QLtPJiDg=/aHR0cHM6Ly9zdWJzdGFja2Nkbi5jb20vaW1hZ2UvZmV0Y2gvd18xNDU2LGNfbGltaXQsZl93ZWJwLHFfYXV0bzpnb29kLGZsX3Byb2dyZXNzaXZlOnN0ZWVwL2h0dHBzJTNBJTJGJTJGc3Vic3RhY2stcG9zdC1tZWRpYS5zMy5hbWF6b25hd3MuY29tJTJGcHVibGljJTJGaW1hZ2VzJTJGOThhMWU1NWQtNzg4My00YzY3LThkN2ItNmUwMjQzMDlmZWQ1XzExNjZ4NjQ2LnBuZw== 1456w" sizes="100vw"/><img src="https://reader.miniflux." alt="" srcset="https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/nVA89jU4u_sz2JH9RWhnP68EEDs7GSVwUz8Ygh3B-Fw=/aHR0cHM6Ly9zdWJzdGFja2Nkbi5jb20vaW1hZ2UvZmV0Y2gvd180MjQsY19saW1pdCxmX2F1dG8scV9hdXRvOmdvb2QsZmxfcHJvZ3Jlc3NpdmU6c3RlZXAvaHR0cHMlM0ElMkYlMkZzdWJzdGFjay1wb3N0LW1lZGlhLnMzLmFtYXpvbmF3cy5jb20lMkZwdWJsaWMlMkZpbWFnZXMlMkY5OGExZTU1ZC03ODgzLTRjNjctOGQ3Yi02ZTAyNDMwOWZlZDVfMTE2Nng2NDYucG5n 424w, https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/2rDyA9k2WkRQnyxbUtc7zpiY- 848w, https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/GNelTfnT200MWkqdjDvyQ-N2v9OfQL3l-8497frVLUk=/aHR0cHM6Ly9zdWJzdGFja2Nkbi5jb20vaW1hZ2UvZmV0Y2gvd18xMjcyLGNfbGltaXQsZl9hdXRvLHFfYXV0bzpnb29kLGZsX3Byb2dyZXNzaXZlOnN0ZWVwL2h0dHBzJTNBJTJGJTJGc3Vic3RhY2stcG9zdC1tZWRpYS5zMy5hbWF6b25hd3MuY29tJTJGcHVibGljJTJGaW1hZ2VzJTJGOThhMWU1NWQtNzg4My00YzY3LThkN2ItNmUwMjQzMDlmZWQ1XzExNjZ4NjQ2LnBuZw== 1272w, https://reader.miniflux. 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"/></picture></a></figure><p>In the 1980s when Roy first coined the idea of “de-development” her aim was to insist that Gaza was not developing even though incomes were growing. Since 2014 even that seems over-optimistic. The Gaza economy as such has been extinguished. When people speak of an “open-air prison” they barely exaggerate. </p><p>In the final edition of Roy’s ground-breaking work, which appeared in 2016:</p><blockquote><p>she argues that Gaza’s trajectory over the last 48 years has reconstructed the territory from one that had been economically integrated and deeply dependent upon Israel and strongly tied to the West Bank, to an isolated and disposable enclave cut off from the West Bank as well as Israel and subject to ongoing military attacks.</p></blockquote><p>So, this is the answer to our question. This is how half the population of Gaza can simply be ordered to move from one end of the enclave to the other. The civilians have no wealth to speak of and few or any connections with the outside world. They depend, in any case on aid and what little they can smuggle in. They have become, as Roy so presciently put it, “isolated and disposable”. At this moment of crisis, the IDF would prefer not to have them in the way, when what it wants to concentrate on doing is killing Hamas fighters and destroying their military infrastructure. So it is time for them to move. </p><p>***</p><p>Cameron Abadi and I did a podcast <a href="https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/the-economics-of-the-israel-hamas-war/id1584397047?i=1000631197543" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="no-referrer">here</a>:</p><p><a href="https://adamtooze.substack.com/subscribe?" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="no-referrer">Subscribe now</a></p><p> </p>